Component `SvgCanvas`:
```
function SvgCanvas({sheets}:{sheets:Sheet[]}){
 return (
  <svg width="100%" viewBox={`0 0 ${sheet.W} ${sheet.H}`}>...</svg>
 );
}
```
• Scale factor so 2440 mm → 800 px max.
• Each rect: `<rect x y width height class="fill-slate-100 stroke-gray-700"/>`
• Label: `<text dominant-baseline="middle" text-anchor="middle">ID\nW×H</text>` using `<tspan>`.
• Show waste % per sheet bottom-right.
• Theme with Tailwind. Allow click to highlight part.

